{"type": "article", "id": 34567, "title": "Hugo Boss进一步降价，以及，Vetements 的红丝带背包有意思 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-17T02:43:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 34952, "name": "Apple 表带"}, {"id": 34953, "name": "红丝带"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 3113, "name": "Salvatore Ferragamo"}, {"id": 9760, "name": "TOMS"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 34954, "name": "Kenneth Cole"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161117100821oWYS5s9wyHX2UKZv.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/hugo-boss-to-simplify-brand-portfolio-and-adjust-prices/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hugo Boss 要品牌重塑，调整价格</b></a> | Hugo Boss 新的首席执行官 Mark Langer 称，公司计划进行品牌重塑，调整价格，以适应更年轻的消费者。与此同时，更为年轻的 Hugo 支线将以“提供负担得起的时尚”为目标，价格调整至比 Boss 支线低 30%。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-11-15/ferragamo-plummets-after-sales-falloff-sparks-christmas-concern\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Salvatore Ferragamo 第三季度业绩大跌 19%</b></a> | 意大利奢侈品牌 Salvatore Ferragamo 第三季度的销售额大跌 19%，收入下跌了 6.2%。该公司称，由于第三季度的销售低于预期，库存过高，它将在圣诞季进行大幅度折扣以清理库存。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/kenneth-cole-to-close-all-its-outlet-stores-in-the-u-s/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Kenneth Cole 关闭美国的所有折扣店</b></a> | 1982 年创立于纽约的时尚女装品牌 Kenneth Cole 日前宣布，要关闭它在美国的所有折扣店，把精力转向电商网络和海外店铺的发展上。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/vetements-x-eastpak-pakr-backpack\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国箱包品牌 EASTPAK 邀请了 12 位设计师，展开了一个名为 Artist Studio Collection 的企划</a>。其中就包括 Vetements 的创始人 Demna Gvasalia。Demna Gvasalia 从红丝带汲取灵感，以夸张的 oversized 造型打造背包的背带和手柄。参与这个 Artist Studio Collection 企划的设计师和品牌还包括 KENZO、Christopher Raeburn、Nicopanda 与 Giambattista Valli 等，全新系列将于 12 月 1 日公开拍卖，所得钱款会捐赠给 Designers Against Aids Foundation 慈善基金会。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093705DipGZwMxuKglBq2j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666425\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611170937143cKONSsCrWuyg1LG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093714Q2nTJcXuWwyqeHRZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093714rvOKQtupYzU91DSl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/ronnie-fieg-x-asics-tiger-gel-lyte-iii-i-teaser\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计师 Ronnie Fieg 曝光 KITH 与 ASICS Tiger GEL-Lyte 3.1 联名鞋款</a>，这双鞋以浅橙色为主调，麂皮鞋身辅以双方的 logo 点缀。它保留了 ASICIS Tiger 的经典鞋身轮廓，鞋底改用了 GEL-Nimbus，显得更前卫。这双鞋将于 11 月 22 日正式发布。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093740X9OjoxwRc6nFTiVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/dior-by-christian-dior/\" rel=\"nofollow\">庆祝品牌成立 70 周年，Dior 推出《Dior by Christian Dior》专书</a>，这本书的内容包括 Christian Dior 生前发表的每一个高级定制系列，由 1947 年的春夏系列一直到他的最后一个 1957 年秋冬系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093646hLzQrV7PqvZXAJnY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093647LHYtk3WobTPGnVfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093646JVA3psX5SQz9HEtf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093647Zi25CfrwxFoVzGMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093647fYhZnMtN0L3GW1Re.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093647dDLkvHYbXc1wh4Mm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093647ksr9yvtLUo1jhaQZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093648b04zuZjTU8Y9c1lg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093648yVMcdreH97EK4LDi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093654JVfFY5pbC6R8lzMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">喜欢休闲运动风的话，诞生于东京的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/sayhello-2016-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">SAYHELLO</a> 是个不错的选择，它主打街头潮流，最近发布的 2016 秋冬季系列就挺好看的。值得一提的是，SAYHELLO 并没有自己的独立门店，不过你倒是可以在日本街头的各大买手店，比如 BEAMS、DICE&amp;DICE 里面找到它。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093600I4tVWbcQEeaoshPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093613O4Q5hpwRlysTqJvK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093614H6FYwAjDxzmJXNG4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093614OvkpCYSfte1RjXyM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611170936250f1Mogh9qwsuSeXT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093625lO7TcCSvBPX62fMa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093635AClvBt5wghSu8sYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/11/16/toms-apple-watch-bands/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TOMS 正式推出 Apple Watch 表带计划</a>，协助公益团体 SolarAid 与 Solar Sister。承诺每售出一款 Apple Watch 表带，就会提供一年的太阳能电源给一个有需要的人。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093529j09h7DA4XitJ1fUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093529dZilWRGEB6rHXjo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093537od3cRTaIre52Oqsi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093538rmGOzAPjKqhI2HiV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117093538Os7rmTk4XREGtoLB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}